WEBVTT

01:53.479 --> 01:54.920
I, Fei Zheng, swear

01:55.150 --> 01:56.590
that even though I am in Jinglan,

01:56.590 --> 01:59.070
I will obey Changmo’s orders
at all times,

01:59.280 --> 02:00.400
even at the cost of my life.

02:00.400 --> 02:01.350
If I break this vow,

02:01.350 --> 02:03.150
may I die without a burial place.

02:09.520 --> 02:10.310
This token

02:10.800 --> 02:12.710
represents the King of Mo himself.

02:12.710 --> 02:13.770
You recognized me.

02:13.870 --> 02:16.000
I believe when we first met,

02:17.190 --> 02:18.520
you recognized me, too.

02:19.430 --> 02:20.430
As Changmo’s

02:20.430 --> 02:22.230
deepest-placed spy in Jinglan,

02:23.150 --> 02:25.480
how could you forget an old acquaintance?

02:26.150 --> 02:27.079
What do you want?

02:27.280 --> 02:29.870
You have been undercover
in Jinglan for years.

02:29.870 --> 02:30.470
And now,

02:30.800 --> 02:32.590
you are the Minister of Revenue.

02:32.590 --> 02:33.910
The Hall Master believes

02:33.910 --> 02:35.370
it’s time to activate you.

02:38.590 --> 02:41.050
What makes you think
I’ll let him control me?

02:41.750 --> 02:43.010
You swore a blood oath.

02:43.310 --> 02:44.310
Blood oath?

02:44.750 --> 02:46.680
You know what happens to traitors.

02:47.280 --> 02:49.310
Do you want me to fail the mission

02:49.750 --> 02:50.960
and end up like them?

03:01.590 --> 03:02.240
Tell me.

03:03.470 --> 03:05.530
What mission did you bring this time?

03:05.630 --> 03:07.160
First, escort the princess

03:07.240 --> 03:08.240
safely to Jinglan

03:08.840 --> 03:10.370
for the marriage alliance.

03:11.080 --> 03:11.810
The second is

03:14.240 --> 03:15.040
to awaken you.

03:16.240 --> 03:18.750
Years of planning have now
been set in motion.

03:18.750 --> 03:20.810
There’s no turning back for any of us.

03:33.470 --> 03:34.150
Stop!

03:34.360 --> 03:35.120
Stop!

03:35.190 --> 03:35.850
Don't move!

03:36.000 --> 03:36.470
Stop!

03:36.710 --> 03:38.520
Stop. Stop right there!

03:38.750 --> 03:39.750
Everybody, stop!

03:42.630 --> 03:43.360
Stop!

03:43.960 --> 03:44.680
Don't move!

03:45.190 --> 03:46.750
Every mountain has its master,

03:46.750 --> 03:47.630
What happened?

03:47.630 --> 03:48.680
and every road has its lord.

03:48.680 --> 03:49.360
Don't worry.

03:49.360 --> 03:50.030
Today,

03:50.030 --> 03:50.710
They are just a few bandits.

03:50.710 --> 03:52.190
if you want to pass,

03:52.360 --> 03:54.710
leave your money behind.

03:59.680 --> 04:01.140
Do you even know who we are?

04:01.240 --> 04:03.370
You dare to rob government officials?

04:04.590 --> 04:06.150
They are government officials.

04:06.150 --> 04:06.750
So what?

04:07.030 --> 04:08.560
So what if they are government officials?

04:08.560 --> 04:09.590
We outnumber them.

04:09.590 --> 04:10.680
Yes, we are not afraid of you.

04:10.680 --> 04:11.630
We have more people!

04:11.630 --> 04:13.080
We are almost at the capital.

04:13.080 --> 04:14.400
How could something like this happen?

04:14.400 --> 04:15.750
West of the capital
isn’t like the main pass.

04:15.750 --> 04:17.310
These are narrow backroads.

04:17.310 --> 04:19.160
In these remote
and impoverished backwaters,

04:19.160 --> 04:21.600
it is inevitable that ruffians
will commit evil deeds.

04:21.600 --> 04:22.130
Hurry up.

04:24.040 --> 04:24.700
Chengfeng.

04:24.830 --> 04:25.920
Yes, General.

04:33.870 --> 04:34.430
Boss.

04:34.680 --> 04:35.210
Get them!

04:35.270 --> 04:35.750
Get them!

04:35.750 --> 04:36.870
G-Get them!

04:42.870 --> 04:43.310
Run!

04:43.870 --> 04:44.360
Run!

04:46.920 --> 04:47.850
Mercy, my lords!

04:48.159 --> 04:48.720
Stop hitting us.

04:48.720 --> 04:49.360
Stop hitting us.

04:49.360 --> 04:51.159
Highway robbery is a capital offense.

04:51.159 --> 04:52.560
Do you still want to live?

04:52.680 --> 04:53.950
We had no choice.

04:54.310 --> 04:56.480
Last month, an official came,

04:56.560 --> 04:58.720
saying he was a servant
of Lord Wang from the court.

04:58.720 --> 05:00.310
He set their sights on our village land.

05:00.310 --> 05:02.070
He claimed our village
had excellent feng shui

05:02.070 --> 05:03.310
and wanted to build a tomb

05:03.310 --> 05:05.160
for Lord Wang’s
recently deceased concubine.

05:05.160 --> 05:05.680
So,

05:05.680 --> 05:07.680
they drove all of us out.

05:07.800 --> 05:08.830
Yes, yes, yes.

05:10.190 --> 05:10.790
Lord Wang?

05:11.240 --> 05:11.950
Wang Ruhai?

05:12.040 --> 05:14.310
One of the 3 ministers appointed
by the late emperor—

05:14.310 --> 05:15.440
If I'm not mistaken,

05:15.630 --> 05:16.290
that's him.

05:17.040 --> 05:18.600
What a scoundrel.

05:19.270 --> 05:21.330
Even his servant dares
to seize land.

05:21.430 --> 05:23.040
We only rob the rich to help the poor.

05:23.040 --> 05:24.040
We only rob the rich.

05:24.040 --> 05:25.310
We let the poor go.

05:25.510 --> 05:26.560
-Yes.
-My lords.

05:26.560 --> 05:28.020
Please spare us this time.

05:28.680 --> 05:30.080
Why should I believe you?

05:32.000 --> 05:32.750
Stop hiding.

05:32.750 --> 05:33.360
Come out.

05:33.360 --> 05:34.000
Come ou!.

05:34.070 --> 05:35.240
E-Everyone, come out.

05:35.240 --> 05:36.870
E-Everyone, come out.

05:43.310 --> 05:44.170
Look, my lords,

05:44.310 --> 05:45.640
what we said is all true.

05:48.120 --> 05:48.780
Chengfeng.

05:49.120 --> 05:49.650
Yes, sir.

05:50.310 --> 05:51.510
Give them some money.

05:52.240 --> 05:52.770
Yes, sir.

05:56.480 --> 05:57.510
Take this money

05:58.270 --> 06:00.000
and find a place to settle down.

06:01.120 --> 06:02.560
Someone will see justice done for you.

06:02.560 --> 06:03.510
Thank you, my lords.

06:03.510 --> 06:04.360
Thank you, my lords.

06:04.360 --> 06:05.870
Thank you, my lords.

06:06.120 --> 06:07.520
-Let's go.
-Don't worry.

06:07.680 --> 06:09.240
When we return to the capital,

06:09.240 --> 06:12.170
I will report this matter truthfully
to His Majesty.

06:13.270 --> 06:14.040
Let me say it.

06:14.510 --> 06:15.110
After all,

06:15.310 --> 06:17.120
you have to work with them in the court,

06:17.120 --> 06:18.920
while I am far away at the border.

06:20.070 --> 06:20.430
Hyah!

06:23.390 --> 06:23.830
Hyah!

06:29.000 --> 06:29.330
Look.

06:29.750 --> 06:30.600
So?

06:30.800 --> 06:33.000
Do I carry myself like the Son of Heaven?

06:33.159 --> 06:34.480
Your Majesty, you were born

06:34.480 --> 06:36.510
with the bearing of the Son of Heaven.

06:36.510 --> 06:37.310
Of course.

06:41.120 --> 06:43.360
Greetings, Your Majesty.

06:44.159 --> 06:44.890
You are here.

06:45.159 --> 06:46.159
Come, take a look.

06:46.270 --> 06:47.720
If I wear this

06:47.920 --> 06:50.250
to welcome General Xiao, how does it look?

06:50.750 --> 06:51.560
Your Majesty.

06:52.159 --> 06:54.000
Why is there no morning court today?

06:54.000 --> 06:55.680
Where have

06:56.159 --> 06:57.190
all the ministers gone?

06:57.190 --> 06:57.750
Today,

06:57.920 --> 06:59.310
Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng

06:59.310 --> 07:00.920
are escorting the princess back.

07:00.920 --> 07:01.720
I sent them

07:01.720 --> 07:03.190
to the city gates to welcome them.

07:03.190 --> 07:04.360
Once they are welcomed back,

07:04.360 --> 07:06.160
-we will...
-Since ancient times,

07:06.160 --> 07:08.000
the state has always come first.

07:08.120 --> 07:08.920
Your Majesty,

07:09.040 --> 07:11.800
how could you dismiss the court

07:11.800 --> 07:14.680
to welcome a border general?

07:14.920 --> 07:16.240
Yes, Your Majesty.

07:16.480 --> 07:18.190
Xiao Chi is nothing but a brute soldier.

07:18.190 --> 07:19.510
What right does he have

07:19.510 --> 07:21.430
to have so many court ministers

07:21.430 --> 07:23.120
welcome him together?

07:23.390 --> 07:25.680
This is against proper court etiquette.

07:26.070 --> 07:27.870
Yes, you are the lord,

07:28.070 --> 07:29.310
and he is the subject.

07:29.630 --> 07:32.000
Doing this will only fuel

07:32.159 --> 07:34.430
his arrogance.

07:35.070 --> 07:36.720
Yes, Your Majesty.

07:37.190 --> 07:37.990
Your Majesty.

07:38.190 --> 07:40.560
Do you know where this is?

07:42.270 --> 07:43.310
This is

07:45.040 --> 07:46.310
the Hall of Diligent Governance.

07:46.310 --> 07:48.000
For the sake of a mere warrior,

07:48.190 --> 07:50.190
you would even skip court.

07:50.800 --> 07:55.200
Well, the Hall of Diligent Governance
will have to change its name afterwards.

07:55.750 --> 07:57.750
Seeing Your Majesty like this,

07:58.159 --> 07:59.270
we have truly

07:59.510 --> 08:02.560
failed the late emperor’s trust.

08:02.870 --> 08:04.430
Even after we die,

08:04.600 --> 08:07.800
we will be too ashamed
to face the late emperor.

08:07.870 --> 08:09.800
We have failed the late emperor.

08:09.800 --> 08:11.800
It won’t come to that, surely.

08:12.240 --> 08:13.920
Next time, before making such decisions,

08:13.920 --> 08:16.600
I will consult with you first.

08:16.950 --> 08:18.270
Next time?

08:18.870 --> 08:20.870
What about this time?

08:21.190 --> 08:23.750
Your Majesty, you are the Son of Heaven,

08:23.750 --> 08:25.560
even you should be punished

08:25.600 --> 08:27.240
for wrongdoing.

08:27.510 --> 08:29.630
Y-Yes, exactly.

08:31.270 --> 08:32.270
What punishment?

08:33.909 --> 08:34.669
Well...

08:35.320 --> 08:36.150
How about this?

08:36.150 --> 08:37.390
Your Majesty shall be punished

08:37.390 --> 08:40.789
to copy the late Emperor's instructions
10 times.

08:41.030 --> 08:42.240
10 times?

08:42.440 --> 08:42.750
Yes.

08:42.870 --> 08:43.320
Yes.

08:43.960 --> 08:45.270
Only after completing them

08:45.270 --> 08:47.840
may you see Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng.

08:48.320 --> 08:48.960
Okay.

08:49.790 --> 08:50.600
I understand.

08:52.910 --> 08:55.360
We will take our leave.

08:55.440 --> 08:57.320
I... I shall take my leave.

08:57.320 --> 08:58.320
Take my leave.

09:06.960 --> 09:08.270
What are you looking at me for?

09:08.270 --> 09:10.470
Prepare the writing materials at once.

09:10.600 --> 09:11.660
Yes, Your Majesty.

09:25.320 --> 09:28.790
Welcome back to the capital, Lord Fei.

09:29.200 --> 09:32.510
Welcome back to the capital, General Xiao.

09:35.000 --> 09:35.320
Wow.

09:35.720 --> 09:37.320
-Is this...
-Your Highness.

09:49.120 --> 09:50.600
His Majesty decrees:

09:50.790 --> 09:54.080
Princess Peace of Changmo shall stay
at the post house temporarily.

09:54.080 --> 09:57.540
Lord Fei and General Xiao are
to enter the palace immediately.

09:58.870 --> 10:00.200
We obey His Majesty's command.

10:00.200 --> 10:02.320
It’s quite different from Changmo.

10:04.440 --> 10:06.240
It is.

10:08.750 --> 10:10.350
What are they talking about?

10:10.750 --> 10:11.610
Your Highness.

10:11.790 --> 10:13.080
Mind your conduct.

10:15.600 --> 10:16.260
Chengfeng,

10:16.480 --> 10:19.200
have Physician Han stay
at the post house with the princess.

10:19.200 --> 10:19.910
Keep an eye on them.

10:19.910 --> 10:20.630
I will return shortly.

10:20.630 --> 10:21.430
Yes, General.

10:22.120 --> 10:22.650
Let's go.

10:30.750 --> 10:35.120
Long live the Emperor!

10:35.440 --> 10:35.910
Rise.

10:36.270 --> 10:37.200
Rise, all of you.

10:38.870 --> 10:39.510
Xiao Chi.

10:40.150 --> 10:40.750
Fei Zheng.

10:41.600 --> 10:43.030
You two have traveled a long way.

10:43.030 --> 10:44.240
You must be weary from the journey.

10:44.240 --> 10:45.500
I missed Your Majesty,

10:45.750 --> 10:47.750
so I hastened back without delay.

10:48.120 --> 10:49.480
It's good that you're back.

10:49.480 --> 10:50.360
General Xiao,

10:50.750 --> 10:52.630
you've guarded the border for years

10:52.630 --> 10:54.320
and made great contributions.

10:54.320 --> 10:54.960
Next,

10:55.240 --> 10:58.300
I intend to have you transfer
to the capital's defense.

10:58.600 --> 11:00.730
Don't go back to Tianlang Pass for now.

11:01.200 --> 11:02.000
Your Majesty.

11:02.600 --> 11:05.670
General Xiao has guarded Tianlang Pass
for years.

11:05.790 --> 11:09.390
Replacing a general
at such a time is a grave taboo.

11:09.790 --> 11:10.550
Yes.

11:11.200 --> 11:12.320
Lord Zhang,

11:12.750 --> 11:13.950
you made a fair point.

11:14.550 --> 11:15.350
Your Majesty.

11:15.790 --> 11:17.120
the Princess of Changmo

11:17.510 --> 11:19.030
has safely arrived in the capital.

11:19.030 --> 11:20.600
We await Your Majesty’s instruction

11:20.600 --> 11:22.120
for the marriage alliance.

11:22.120 --> 11:23.870
It's good that you brought her back.

11:23.870 --> 11:26.670
The marriage alliance needs
to be arranged carefully.

11:26.670 --> 11:28.000
This marriage alliance

11:28.030 --> 11:31.270
must be conducted according
to Jinglan rites.

11:31.840 --> 11:33.570
Lord Wang is absolutely right.

11:33.840 --> 11:36.150
The etiquette of Jinglan
is extremely complex.

11:36.150 --> 11:38.390
As the acting Minister of Rites,

11:38.510 --> 11:40.670
it indeed requires careful consideration.

11:40.670 --> 11:41.510
Yes.

11:42.790 --> 11:45.910
General Xiao, you've faced Changmo
for years.

11:46.270 --> 11:47.630
Returning this time,

11:47.670 --> 11:49.790
do you have any good news for us?

11:49.870 --> 11:51.270
Any news from the border?

11:51.550 --> 11:53.720
Changmo has invaded repeatedly
but never broken through.

11:53.720 --> 11:54.980
Thanks to His Majesty,

11:55.030 --> 11:56.030
the people live in peace,

11:56.030 --> 11:57.390
and we have bountiful harvests every year.

11:57.390 --> 11:58.050
Would these

11:58.390 --> 12:00.600
count as good news, Lord Wang?

12:00.960 --> 12:02.000
Yes, yes, yes.

12:02.440 --> 12:03.080
Oh, right.

12:03.510 --> 12:05.310
I have 2 more pieces of good news.

12:05.960 --> 12:07.890
I brought the Border Special Envoy

12:08.120 --> 12:09.390
Zhao Gao back with me.

12:09.480 --> 12:10.240
Lord Wang,

12:10.480 --> 12:12.600
you can catch up with him.

12:13.550 --> 12:16.030
His Majesty didn't summon him back.

12:16.630 --> 12:18.630
How could you act on your own

12:18.630 --> 12:20.320
and bring him back to the capital?

12:20.320 --> 12:21.200
Zhao Gao,

12:21.510 --> 12:23.600
went to the border as a Special Envoy

12:24.120 --> 12:25.630
but never visited the military camp.

12:25.630 --> 12:27.240
He drank and made merry every day,

12:27.240 --> 12:30.240
and even tried to force
a Changmo woman into marriage.

12:31.240 --> 12:34.720
He was merely negligent on occasion.

12:34.910 --> 12:35.440
Does that

12:35.670 --> 12:37.550
violate your military law?

12:37.840 --> 12:39.480
In our Jinglan military law,

12:39.480 --> 12:42.840
which clause forbids drinking at home

12:42.870 --> 12:46.120
or marrying a woman from an enemy state?

12:46.910 --> 12:47.510
Lord Wang,

12:47.910 --> 12:49.870
you are indeed very protective
of your nephew.

12:49.870 --> 12:50.390
Yes.

12:51.030 --> 12:52.360
I haven't finished yet.

12:53.240 --> 12:54.000
Zhao Gao

12:54.200 --> 12:56.240
embezzled 800,000 taels of military funds.

12:56.240 --> 12:58.600
Lord Wang, you must
have had a hand in this.

13:03.320 --> 13:04.080
Xiao Chi,

13:04.600 --> 13:06.080
what nonsense are you talking about?

13:06.080 --> 13:08.150
I know nothing of this matter.

13:08.750 --> 13:09.870
Do you really not know?

13:09.870 --> 13:10.150
I...

13:11.320 --> 13:11.600
I...

13:12.120 --> 13:12.840
don't know!

13:13.630 --> 13:14.390
Fine.

13:14.840 --> 13:16.970
I'll assume you don't know, Lord Wang.

13:18.240 --> 13:21.000
Yet you permitted your servants
to forcibly seize land in Qingshan Village

13:21.000 --> 13:22.670
to build a tomb for your concubine.

13:22.670 --> 13:24.470
You must know about that, right?

13:24.600 --> 13:25.270
The villagers were driven
from their homes

13:25.270 --> 13:26.390
and left destitute.

13:26.390 --> 13:28.030
I saw this with my own eyes.

13:28.960 --> 13:31.630
You sent your nephew
to the border as a Special Envoy.

13:31.630 --> 13:32.630
If he abided by the law

13:32.630 --> 13:34.120
and rendered distinguished service,

13:34.120 --> 13:35.720
it would have counted
as a great merit to your name.

13:35.720 --> 13:38.510
But he embezzled 800,000 taels
of military funds.

13:38.510 --> 13:40.270
And you permitted your servants
to seize land,

13:40.270 --> 13:42.000
leaving the people destitute.

13:42.600 --> 13:43.200
You are a key minister appointed

13:43.200 --> 13:45.530
by the late Emperor to assist His Majesty.

13:45.670 --> 13:47.030
For committing such acts,

13:47.030 --> 13:48.830
what punishment do you deserve?

13:49.720 --> 13:50.720
Do calm yourself.

13:51.600 --> 13:52.360
Xiao Chi,

13:52.550 --> 13:53.720
as soon as you return,

13:53.720 --> 13:56.720
you openly accuse a senior minister
of the court.

13:57.150 --> 13:59.150
Where does that leave His Majesty?

13:59.630 --> 14:00.910
Where do you put

14:00.910 --> 14:04.200
the 3 ministers entrusted
by the late Emperor

14:04.200 --> 14:05.150
to His Majesty?

14:05.150 --> 14:06.680
-Exactly.
-And Lord Zhang,

14:07.390 --> 14:09.790
what is your attitude towards His Majesty?

14:10.120 --> 14:12.320
Where do you leave His Majesty?

14:12.670 --> 14:14.840
Could it be that Lord Wang’s dealings

14:15.360 --> 14:16.360
also involve you, Lord Zhang?

14:16.360 --> 14:16.820
This...

14:17.080 --> 14:18.240
What are you talking about?

14:18.240 --> 14:19.670
How would I know?

14:19.910 --> 14:20.670
In that case,

14:21.270 --> 14:22.440
I respectfully request Your Majesty

14:22.440 --> 14:24.600
to strip Wang Ruhai
of his rank and titles.

14:24.600 --> 14:25.870
After the truth is found out,

14:25.870 --> 14:28.360
Your Majesty can decide
how to deal with him.

14:28.790 --> 14:29.270
You—

14:31.790 --> 14:32.670
Your Majesty.

14:33.240 --> 14:34.270
I am wronged!

14:34.550 --> 14:36.550
Xiao Chi is slandering me.

14:36.670 --> 14:38.440
I don't know anything about these things.

14:38.440 --> 14:40.480
I don't know them at all!

14:42.080 --> 14:42.880
Your Majesty,

14:43.030 --> 14:44.510
Qingshan Village is small,

14:44.510 --> 14:47.710
but who knows how many Qingshan Villages
are behind this.

14:47.840 --> 14:49.910
The matter of military funds
is of great importance.

14:49.910 --> 14:52.200
I think it must be investigated.

14:53.150 --> 14:53.750
Lord Wang,

14:54.670 --> 14:57.150
whether General Xiao
is making false accusations,

14:57.150 --> 15:00.510
once Zhao Gao and the villagers
of Qingshan are interrogated,

15:00.510 --> 15:02.840
His Majesty will give you a fair judgment.

15:03.150 --> 15:04.350
-I...
-Your Majesty.

15:04.960 --> 15:07.000
We are all ministers

15:07.000 --> 15:09.150
entrusted to you by the late emperor.

15:09.150 --> 15:11.630
You must not act on one-sided testimony

15:11.750 --> 15:13.720
and punish anyone of us.

15:13.720 --> 15:14.200
Yeah.

15:14.200 --> 15:15.630
Yes, Your Majesty.

15:18.870 --> 15:19.750
I think

15:20.320 --> 15:22.320
what you all said makes sense.

15:23.080 --> 15:25.270
There is no need to rush to judgment.

15:25.750 --> 15:26.410
Wang Ruhai,

15:27.240 --> 15:28.700
you go home and rest first.

15:29.080 --> 15:31.080
Once the truth is established,

15:31.200 --> 15:32.390
I will make a decision.

15:32.390 --> 15:32.670
I...

15:33.510 --> 15:33.970
This...

15:34.030 --> 15:34.910
He... He...

15:35.240 --> 15:35.750
Your Majesty.

15:35.750 --> 15:36.410
Lord Zhang.

15:37.150 --> 15:39.080
Your Majesty, as the Son of Heaven,

15:39.510 --> 15:41.550
he is also the late emperor’s
sole legitimate successor.

15:41.550 --> 15:44.150
Lord Zhang, are you going
to disobey his order?

15:44.240 --> 15:44.600
I...

15:47.720 --> 15:48.240
Okay.

15:48.720 --> 15:50.120
Then it's settled.

15:50.390 --> 15:50.840
I...

15:51.200 --> 15:52.390
What do you think,

15:52.750 --> 15:53.550
my ministers?

15:54.320 --> 15:56.120
We shall leave it at that for now.

15:59.840 --> 16:01.370
If there are no objections,

16:01.630 --> 16:02.270
the court

16:03.510 --> 16:04.480
is adjourned.

16:05.120 --> 16:07.630
We'll take our leave.

16:09.000 --> 16:10.330
All of you may withdraw.

16:10.630 --> 16:11.510
-Yes.
-Yes.

16:12.120 --> 16:13.270
You, too, get out.

16:13.270 --> 16:13.910
Yes.

16:15.240 --> 16:16.670
Why are you still standing there?

16:16.670 --> 16:17.790
If I leave,

16:17.790 --> 16:19.270
who will attend to Your Majesty?

16:19.270 --> 16:21.200
Just get out when I tell you to.

16:21.200 --> 16:22.790
Why all this talk?

16:22.790 --> 16:23.480
Yes.

16:24.630 --> 16:25.390
Without my orders,

16:25.390 --> 16:26.440
no one is allowed in.

16:26.440 --> 16:27.080
Yes.

16:29.870 --> 16:30.480
All right.

16:31.480 --> 16:32.210
Let's begin.

16:32.320 --> 16:34.440
Just as we did back at the manor.

16:34.840 --> 16:36.840
Like in the manor?

16:37.480 --> 16:39.150
Would this not be against the rules?

16:39.150 --> 16:40.720
Forget the rules.

16:40.720 --> 16:42.380
I have already sent them away.

16:42.630 --> 16:43.750
But... Your Majesty...

16:43.750 --> 16:44.950
What "Your Majesty"?

16:45.200 --> 16:47.840
Xiao Chi, you just got back.
Must you spoil the mood?

16:47.840 --> 16:48.200
Come.

16:48.840 --> 16:50.440
Let's drink a pot right now.

16:50.910 --> 16:53.630
Tonight, we drink until we drop.

16:57.120 --> 16:58.600
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:09.640 --> 17:10.240
It's so late.

17:10.240 --> 17:11.270
Why aren't you going back
to your room to rest?

17:11.270 --> 17:12.869
I'm waiting for the general.

17:12.920 --> 17:13.780
Physician Han.

17:13.920 --> 17:15.510
Are you going out?

17:16.680 --> 17:18.200
I'll go find the general for you,

17:18.200 --> 17:20.060
and tell him to come back earlier.

17:21.160 --> 17:22.020
Physician Han.

17:23.960 --> 17:24.619
Never mind.

17:24.720 --> 17:25.240
You go.

17:41.160 --> 17:41.960
What's wrong?

17:42.110 --> 17:43.710
Is something troubling you?

17:43.720 --> 17:44.180
It's...

17:44.510 --> 17:45.310
It's nothing.

17:48.000 --> 17:49.530
I am already in the capital.

17:49.790 --> 17:51.920
Why hasn’t Liu Chu come to receive me yet?

17:51.920 --> 17:54.070
Your Highness, you can't rush this.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.830
Didn’t Lord Fei say

17:55.920 --> 17:57.200
you’d be welcomed

17:57.350 --> 17:58.950
with full Jinglan ceremony?

17:59.440 --> 18:00.160
I hope so.

18:03.270 --> 18:04.730
It's like this every time.

18:04.960 --> 18:06.560
Xiao Chi and I are both drunk,

18:07.590 --> 18:09.120
but you're not drunk at all.

18:09.400 --> 18:10.880
Yeah, Zheng.

18:12.160 --> 18:13.440
That's not right.

18:14.310 --> 18:17.310
Your Majesty, I just look sober
on the outside.

18:18.000 --> 18:18.480
Look,

18:18.750 --> 18:19.110
I...

18:20.270 --> 18:21.440
can barely stand.

18:22.000 --> 18:22.640
Okay.

18:23.480 --> 18:24.440
Then sit here.

18:26.030 --> 18:26.960
I wouldn't dare.

18:27.160 --> 18:27.750
Look.

18:28.590 --> 18:31.750
He's still talking about etiquette
between ruler and minister.

18:31.750 --> 18:33.350
This means you're not drunk.

18:35.310 --> 18:37.920
Xiao Chi, thanks to you being here today.

18:38.160 --> 18:40.090
You help me teach him a harsh lesson

18:40.270 --> 18:41.550
and vent this anger.

18:42.550 --> 18:43.070
C...

18:44.350 --> 18:44.960
Chu,

18:45.720 --> 18:46.830
it's my duty.

18:47.440 --> 18:48.770
That was so satisfying.

18:49.720 --> 18:52.960
I must reward you handsomely.

18:53.640 --> 18:54.310
Reward me?

18:54.440 --> 18:55.160
Yes.

18:57.070 --> 18:57.930
I don't need it.

18:58.030 --> 18:58.680
No.

18:59.200 --> 19:00.860
What should I reward you with?

19:03.350 --> 19:03.960
The token.

19:05.270 --> 19:06.750
Seeing this token

19:07.070 --> 19:09.070
is like seeing the Emperor himself.

19:09.350 --> 19:11.030
In the entire capital city,

19:11.200 --> 19:12.920
you can go wherever you want.

19:14.830 --> 19:15.350
Then,

19:16.790 --> 19:17.960
thank you, Chu.

19:18.960 --> 19:20.160
I originally thought

19:21.000 --> 19:22.440
I would be

19:22.750 --> 19:25.270
a very happy and carefree prince.

19:25.920 --> 19:26.880
I didn't expect

19:27.440 --> 19:29.900
my father to suddenly
fall ill and pass away,

19:30.350 --> 19:31.750
passing the throne to me.

19:34.110 --> 19:36.040
I've never been an emperor before.

19:36.480 --> 19:38.080
How would I know how to be one?

19:39.000 --> 19:39.480
Chu,

19:40.240 --> 19:41.440
no matter where I am,

19:42.240 --> 19:43.900
no matter what you ask me to do,

19:45.750 --> 19:46.640
I, Xiao Chi,

19:47.110 --> 19:48.640
will serve you with my life.

19:48.830 --> 19:50.360
You always know what to say.

19:52.790 --> 19:54.050
Then you get him drunk.

19:56.920 --> 19:59.240
Get him drunk? No need.

19:59.550 --> 20:00.720
Drink up, Zheng.

20:00.920 --> 20:02.000
Okay, okay, okay.

20:02.790 --> 20:04.270
I accept my punishment.

20:09.830 --> 20:12.240
It seems we are no match for him at all.

20:12.550 --> 20:13.720
We can't outdrink him.

20:13.720 --> 20:15.270
We can only find a chance—

20:15.270 --> 20:17.800
when all the officials
are drinking with you,

20:18.070 --> 20:19.470
then we’ll get him drunk.

20:19.790 --> 20:20.920
A chance?

20:21.720 --> 20:22.830
What kind of chancer?

20:22.830 --> 20:25.110
Why not

20:26.480 --> 20:27.790
on Chi’s wedding day?

20:30.680 --> 20:31.400
Wedding?

20:31.720 --> 20:32.400
Yes.

20:33.110 --> 20:33.920
Well...

20:34.030 --> 20:36.240
Do you have a woman you like?

20:41.640 --> 20:42.590
No.

20:42.960 --> 20:43.640
No?

20:44.310 --> 20:45.960
All the women at the border

20:46.110 --> 20:47.680
want to marry General Xiao.

20:48.480 --> 20:49.280
Zheng, you...

20:49.590 --> 20:50.790
What nonsense are you talking about?

20:50.790 --> 20:52.240
Good for you, Xiao Chi.

20:52.790 --> 20:53.880
Not bad!

20:55.550 --> 20:56.160
Chu,

20:56.510 --> 20:57.880
I might be a bit

20:57.880 --> 20:58.590
drunk.

20:59.030 --> 21:00.430
I'll take my leave first.

21:03.030 --> 21:04.350
I'll take my leave first.

21:04.350 --> 21:04.720
We...

21:05.750 --> 21:07.590
We haven't finished the wine.

21:07.590 --> 21:08.240
Xiao Chi.

21:08.920 --> 21:10.110
General Xiao.

21:11.160 --> 21:11.640
This kid.

21:11.640 --> 21:12.440
Stop yelling.

21:12.590 --> 21:13.200
Do

21:13.550 --> 21:15.920
you have a woman you like?

21:16.920 --> 21:17.270
Chu.

21:17.510 --> 21:17.960
Yeah?

21:18.200 --> 21:19.330
I'll go get him back.

21:19.590 --> 21:20.200
Hey.

21:21.830 --> 21:22.830
Don't worry, Chu.

21:23.000 --> 21:24.730
I will definitely get him back.

21:26.110 --> 21:26.640
Xiao Chi.

21:27.680 --> 21:30.400
Then you guys can drink
with me another day.

21:32.720 --> 21:33.440
Buns!

21:33.440 --> 21:34.070
Come, drink.

21:34.070 --> 21:35.330
Freshly steamed buns!

21:35.400 --> 21:36.530
Get me another bowl.

21:38.160 --> 21:38.880
Buns!

21:39.240 --> 21:40.310
Fresh meat buns!

21:40.440 --> 21:41.160
Not bad.

21:41.200 --> 21:41.720
Miss,

21:42.000 --> 21:43.440
try a meat bun.

21:43.960 --> 21:44.720
Look.

21:47.030 --> 21:47.440
Ma'am,

21:47.640 --> 21:48.770
2 meat buns, please.

21:49.880 --> 21:50.400
Not bad—

21:50.920 --> 21:51.580
her figure.

21:52.790 --> 21:54.310
Do you know where the Imperial Prison is?

21:54.310 --> 21:55.400
The Imperial Prison?

21:55.400 --> 21:56.730
The Imperial Prison...

21:58.200 --> 21:58.800
Thank you.

22:02.200 --> 22:02.590
Go.

22:03.680 --> 22:04.640
Don't go.

22:04.920 --> 22:05.960
Where are you going?

22:05.960 --> 22:08.030
Ask me if you want to go somewhere.

22:08.440 --> 22:09.310
In the capital,

22:09.310 --> 22:11.790
there is nowhere I can't go.

22:12.200 --> 22:15.260
I'm going to the Imperial Prison.
Can you take me there?

22:15.550 --> 22:16.720
That's a good place.

22:17.070 --> 22:19.790
I’ve never had a woman
in the Imperial Prison before.

22:19.790 --> 22:20.510
Me neither.

22:20.680 --> 22:22.550
Just thinking about it is exciting.

22:22.550 --> 22:23.720
Let's go.

22:24.310 --> 22:24.970
You idiots!

22:25.550 --> 22:26.350
Let me show you

22:26.400 --> 22:27.800
what chili powder can do!

22:31.270 --> 22:31.920
After her!

22:32.070 --> 22:32.480
Hurry!

22:33.240 --> 22:33.570
Hyah!

22:34.160 --> 22:35.160
Stop running! Stop!

22:35.160 --> 22:36.160
Stop right there!

22:38.160 --> 22:39.030
Stop!

22:40.440 --> 22:41.270
I said stop!

22:41.270 --> 22:42.070
I'll kill you!

22:42.160 --> 22:42.640
Bitch!

22:42.880 --> 22:43.590
Stop!

22:43.830 --> 22:44.550
I said stop!

22:45.240 --> 22:45.830
After her!

22:45.830 --> 22:46.160
Hyah!

22:46.240 --> 22:46.750
After her!

22:46.750 --> 22:47.510
Stop!

22:49.350 --> 22:50.550
Still dare to fight back?

22:50.550 --> 22:52.000
I'll break your legs!

22:53.510 --> 22:54.350
Stop!

22:54.510 --> 22:55.110
After her!

22:56.000 --> 22:56.240
Hyah!

22:56.240 --> 22:56.880
Stop!

22:59.400 --> 23:00.860
Where are you going? Stop!

23:01.030 --> 23:01.920
I said stop!

23:03.200 --> 23:03.680
Run.

23:04.200 --> 23:05.000
Keep running.

23:05.240 --> 23:06.110
Why did you stop?

23:06.110 --> 23:07.920
There's a dead end.

23:08.680 --> 23:09.030
What?

23:09.790 --> 23:11.790
You're out of chili powder, aren't you?

23:11.790 --> 23:14.510
Now I can do whatever I want.

23:14.680 --> 23:16.160
She won't be able
to sneak attack us this time.

23:16.160 --> 23:17.200
Come on, get her!

23:32.790 --> 23:35.240
Didn't I tell you to wait
for me at the relay station?

23:35.240 --> 23:36.700
That's just 3 scoundrels.

23:37.440 --> 23:37.920
Fine.

23:38.200 --> 23:39.400
You’re quite capable.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.790
You dared to go
to the Imperial Prison alone

23:40.790 --> 23:42.070
to investigate your brother's case.

23:42.070 --> 23:43.330
You have a lot of nerve.

23:43.480 --> 23:45.510
Will you ride back, or go on foot?

23:46.030 --> 23:47.090
Riding, of course.

24:15.350 --> 24:17.280
Why did you come here again so late?

24:18.720 --> 24:19.980
You've been drinking？

24:21.030 --> 24:21.750
No.

24:25.880 --> 24:26.790
It's so late.

24:28.000 --> 24:29.530
Who were you drinking with?

24:29.790 --> 24:31.720
Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng, of course.

24:32.400 --> 24:33.830
Who else in this world

24:33.830 --> 24:35.240
is worth spending so much time

24:35.240 --> 24:36.700
and drinking so much with?

24:38.000 --> 24:39.330
I am really happy today.

24:39.680 --> 24:41.440
You’re this happy

24:41.720 --> 24:43.200
just because Xiao Chi is back?

24:43.200 --> 24:44.600
Not just because of that.

24:44.750 --> 24:46.880
It's also because he helped you expose

24:47.000 --> 24:49.260
Wang Ruhai's scandal in court, isn't it?

24:49.790 --> 24:50.550
Yes.

24:50.960 --> 24:53.420
You have no idea
how Wang Ruhai looked today—

24:53.750 --> 24:56.280
kneeling on the ground
and begging for mercy.

24:57.000 --> 24:59.350
I never dreamed he would have such a day.

25:00.000 --> 25:02.920
Xiao Chi really helped me vent my anger.

25:04.240 --> 25:05.960
For the first time, I felt

25:06.880 --> 25:09.030
what it's like to be an emperor.

25:14.160 --> 25:15.000
What's wrong?

25:17.030 --> 25:18.110
Aren't you happy?

25:19.640 --> 25:20.920
Did you issue the edict

25:21.640 --> 25:23.770
to recall Xiao Chi from Tianlang Pass?

25:27.440 --> 25:28.400
I think so.

25:29.030 --> 25:30.030
Xiao Chi

25:30.160 --> 25:32.160
is a key minister guarding the border,

25:32.160 --> 25:34.200
not a bodyguard
to escort you for the political marriage.

25:34.200 --> 25:35.350
Aren't you afraid

25:35.510 --> 25:37.590
the Changmo people
will take advantage of his absence?

25:37.590 --> 25:39.200
Before you did anything in the past,

25:39.200 --> 25:41.160
you would always discuss it with me.

25:41.160 --> 25:42.560
Why didn't you this time?

25:42.680 --> 25:43.310
Sister.

25:44.350 --> 25:46.550
It was a spur-of-the-moment decision.

25:47.400 --> 25:49.110
I swear that whatever I do in the future,

25:49.110 --> 25:51.240
I will definitely discuss it with you.

25:51.590 --> 25:52.830
Don't be mad.

25:52.830 --> 25:54.560
I’ll discuss it with you first,

25:54.640 --> 25:55.900
then issue the decree.

25:57.270 --> 25:58.310
You are the Emperor.

25:58.310 --> 25:59.310
You may decide

25:59.720 --> 26:01.070
as you see fit.

26:01.310 --> 26:02.680
You don't need to discuss with me.

26:02.680 --> 26:05.240
But aren't you my sister?

26:05.400 --> 26:06.310
I was wrong.

26:08.400 --> 26:11.160
I swear I'll keep my word from now on.

26:12.000 --> 26:13.480
Please don’t be upset.

26:16.550 --> 26:17.160
Please...

26:19.160 --> 26:20.030
I don't

26:20.030 --> 26:22.360
expect you to discuss everything with me.

26:22.400 --> 26:23.000
And I don't want to be like

26:23.000 --> 26:25.030
the other 3 senior ministers,

26:25.310 --> 26:26.710
forcing you to do things.

26:29.440 --> 26:30.400
In this palace, only you and I

26:30.400 --> 26:32.030
share the Liu bloodline

26:32.590 --> 26:33.880
as true kin.

26:34.750 --> 26:36.160
Isn't everything I do for...

26:36.160 --> 26:37.030
It's all for me.

26:37.030 --> 26:38.640
I know you did all these things

26:38.640 --> 26:39.480
for me.

26:39.640 --> 26:40.590
I understand.

26:40.590 --> 26:42.880
Sister, don't be mad.

26:43.640 --> 26:44.440
I promise

26:44.830 --> 26:46.430
I won't act on my own anymore.

26:46.960 --> 26:47.680
Okay?

26:51.550 --> 26:52.590
Anyway,

26:52.590 --> 26:53.960
I'll only say this once.

26:54.480 --> 26:56.340
It's up to you whether you listen.

27:00.270 --> 27:01.030
Lie down.

27:01.510 --> 27:02.200
Yes.

27:05.880 --> 27:06.720
Sister,

27:07.680 --> 27:10.920
Xiao Chi has been stationed outside
for many years.

27:11.720 --> 27:13.450
What should we reward him with?

27:15.550 --> 27:16.750
You are the emperor.

27:17.070 --> 27:18.470
You decide for yourself.

27:19.350 --> 27:20.310
But

27:20.920 --> 27:23.520
you have always been
in charge of the treasury.

27:23.830 --> 27:25.960
Why don't you decide?

27:28.270 --> 27:29.160
Money

27:29.880 --> 27:31.610
is definitely indispensable.

27:32.440 --> 27:34.700
We have to arrange a place
for him to live.

27:38.920 --> 27:40.310
I have a place in mind.

28:00.160 --> 28:01.880
Xiao Chi...

28:05.200 --> 28:07.200
General Xiao, you are finally here.

28:08.480 --> 28:11.960
These are the rewards
from His Majesty and the Eldest Princess.

28:11.960 --> 28:14.360
Thank His Majesty and the Eldest Princess.

28:15.110 --> 28:16.110
And there's more.

28:16.270 --> 28:17.160
Please take a look.

28:17.160 --> 28:19.160
Are you satisfied with the residence
His Majesty and the Eldest Princess

28:19.160 --> 28:20.160
prepared for you?

28:21.480 --> 28:22.510
Isn't this...

28:22.510 --> 28:24.920
It's the prince's mansion
before His Majesty ascended the throne.

28:24.920 --> 28:26.200
It's yours now.

28:26.240 --> 28:27.160
How can I accept this?

28:27.160 --> 28:29.240
It was His Majesty's
former residence.

28:29.240 --> 28:31.590
These are the orders
of His Majesty and the Eldest Princess.

28:31.590 --> 28:33.160
It's also their goodwill.

28:33.440 --> 28:35.500
General Xiao, please don't decline.

28:35.920 --> 28:36.680
In this capital,

28:36.680 --> 28:38.590
you must have your own residence.

28:38.590 --> 28:40.160
Lord Fei is right.

28:40.310 --> 28:42.270
I’ve carried out
the Eldest Princess’s orders.

28:42.270 --> 28:43.670
I shall take my leave now.

28:44.030 --> 28:44.630
Take care.

28:45.550 --> 28:46.150
Take care.

28:51.240 --> 28:52.480
This mansion is so big.

28:52.480 --> 28:55.160
We couldn't fill it
even if everyone got a room.

28:56.960 --> 28:58.830
Perhaps His Majesty considered this

28:58.830 --> 29:01.510
and let the Princess of Changmo
stay with you temporarily.

29:01.510 --> 29:03.000
That would be inappropriate.

29:03.000 --> 29:04.160
She is getting married soon.

29:04.160 --> 29:05.830
How can she keep living with us?

29:05.830 --> 29:07.110
His Majesty's will is hard to predict.

29:07.110 --> 29:07.960
You heard it, too.

29:07.960 --> 29:09.920
This is also
the Eldest Princess's order.

29:09.920 --> 29:10.480
As for the mansion,

29:10.480 --> 29:11.790
I've already had it cleaned.

29:11.790 --> 29:13.050
As for who lives where,

29:13.200 --> 29:14.860
you can decide that yourself.

29:15.240 --> 29:15.640
Zheng.

29:16.510 --> 29:18.000
Why don't you move in, too?

29:18.510 --> 29:19.750
Why would I move in?

29:19.830 --> 29:21.030
You used to live here.

29:21.270 --> 29:23.680
Besides, you are very familiar
with this place.

29:23.680 --> 29:24.510
You can stay in the South Courtyard.

29:24.510 --> 29:27.110
It's perfect. You can keep
an eye on them for me.

29:27.480 --> 29:28.310
Me keeping an eye on them?

29:28.310 --> 29:29.370
Then it is settled.

29:29.440 --> 29:31.440
I have urgent matters. I'm leaving.

29:34.160 --> 29:35.350
Then where does she stay?

29:35.350 --> 29:35.830
Who?

29:36.880 --> 29:37.790
Physician Han.

29:39.640 --> 29:40.570
East Courtyard.

29:42.640 --> 29:43.570
East Courtyard.

29:45.480 --> 29:46.830
Brat.

29:47.030 --> 29:49.490
Isn't that the courtyard
you used to live in?

29:52.790 --> 29:55.270
Everything you ordered
has been taken care of.

29:55.270 --> 29:56.240
After I left,

29:56.510 --> 29:57.550
I heard General Xiao

29:57.550 --> 29:59.680
also invited Lord Fei to live with him.

30:10.240 --> 30:11.160
This time,

30:12.000 --> 30:14.200
they are revisiting the old place.
